### 2. Protected Review Submission
```php
// Server-side review processing
$clean_input = [
    'rating' => (int)$_POST['rating'],
    'comment' => htmlspecialchars($_POST['comment'], ENT_QUOTES),
    'user' => $_SESSION['verified_user']
];
file_put_contents('reviews.json', json_encode($clean_input, JSON_PRETTY_PRINT));
